{:paths ["src"]
 ;; Composes the already-landed Wave 1-3 pieces (ADR-2607010930 + ADR-2607022600)
 ;; into the actual kotobase XRPC-surface engine: transact/datoms/q/pull over
 ;; quad-store's hot 4-index Arrangement (routed via kqe), persisted as a
